  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Diabellze the White Witch",
      "effect": "(This card is always treated as a \"White Forest\" card.)\nMonsters you control cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects while you control 2 or more \"Diabell\" monsters. You can only use each of the following effects of \"Diabellze the White Witch\" once per turn. You can send 1 Spell/Trap from your hand or field to the GY; Special Summon this card from your hand. If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can send 1 \"Sinful Spoils\" or \"Diabell\" card from your Deck to the GY.",
      "official": false
    },
